'''雷蒙德·麥高文'''（{{lang-en|Raymond McGovern}}，{{bd|1939年|8月25日||}}）是[[美國|美國]]社會運動者，曾在[[中央情報局|中央情報局]]擔任分析師。

== 生平 ==
出生於[[紐約市|紐約市]][[布朗克斯|布朗克斯]]。就讀[[福坦莫大學|福坦莫大學]]<ref>{{Cite web|title=Alumnus Says Activism Requires Courage|url=https://news.fordham.edu/inside-fordham/alumnus-says-activism-requires-courage/|accessdate=2021-02-06|date=2007-06-29|work=Fordham Newsroom|language=en-US|archive-date=2020-08-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200814000140/https://news.fordham.edu/inside-fordham/alumnus-says-activism-requires-courage/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，擁有該校的[[文學士|文學士]]（B.A.）和[[文學碩士|文學碩士]]（M.A.）學位<ref>{{Cite web|title=Bio|url=https://raymcgovern.com/bio/|accessdate=2021-02-06|publisher=Ray McGovern|language=en-US|archive-date=2021-01-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210116190655/https://raymcgovern.com/bio/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

在[[約翰·甘迺迪|甘迺迪]]政府時期加入中央情報局，任職長達二十七年，橫跨了七位[[美國總統|美國總統]]的任期，一直持續到[[喬治·H·W·布希|喬治·H·W·布希]]為止<ref>{{Cite web|title="Intelligent people know that the empire is on the downhill": A veteran CIA agent spills the goods on the Deep State and our foreign policy nightmares|url=https://www.salon.com/2016/02/07/intelligent_people_know_that_the_empire_is_on_the_downhill_a_veteran_cia_agent_spills_the_goods_on_the_deep_state_and_our_foreign_policy_nightmares/|accessdate=2021-02-06|date=2016-02-07|work=Salon|language=en|archive-date=2019-08-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190831104906/https://www.salon.com/2016/02/07/intelligent_people_know_that_the_empire_is_on_the_downhill_a_veteran_cia_agent_spills_the_goods_on_the_deep_state_and_our_foreign_policy_nightmares/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=":0">{{Cite news|url=https://www.upi.com/Defense-News/2006/03/10/The-US-has-run-amok-former-CIA-analyst/87031142051940/?ur3=1|title=The U.S. has run amok; former CIA analyst|date=2006-03-10|work=UPI.com|accessdate=2021-02-07|language=en|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20191006103359/https://www.upi.com/Defense-News/2006/03/10/The-US-has-run-amok-former-CIA-analyst/87031142051940/?ur3=1|archivedate=2019-10-06}}</ref>。

他在1990年從中情局退休時，獲授{{le|情報貢獻獎章|Intelligence Commendation Medal}}。2006年，麥高文退還了該獎章，表示：「我不希望與使用酷刑的機構有任何關連」<ref name=":0" />。

=== 社會運動 ===
[[File:McGovern-Sheehan-Swanson05-18-06.JPG|缩略图]]的示威活動上與反戰運動者[[辛迪·希恩|辛迪·希恩]]和{{le|大衛·史旺森|David Swanson}}在一起。]]
麥高文是[[伊拉克戰爭|伊拉克戰爭]]的反對者。2003年，麥高文與一些前情報人員成立了「Veteran Intelligence Professionals for Sanity」（VIPS），反對伊拉克戰爭<ref name=":0" /><ref>{{Cite news|title=Ex-CIA-Agent zu Überwachung: „Obamas Angst vor Geheimdiensten“|url=https://taz.de/Ex-CIA-Agent-zu-Ueberwachung/!5056027/|newspaper=Die Tageszeitung: taz|date=2013-10-30|accessdate=2021-02-06|language=de|first=Dorothea|last=Hahn|author=|format=|archive-date=2021-05-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210506235647/https://taz.de/Ex-CIA-Agent-zu-Ueberwachung/!5056027/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2006年，麥高文在[[唐納·倫斯斐|唐納·倫斯斐]]的演講中質問他有關伊拉克[[伊拉克與大規模殺傷性武器|大規模殺傷性武器]]的說法<ref>{{Cite web|title=Retired CIA Analyst Ray McGovern Takes on Rumsfeld Over Justification for Iraq Invasion|url=https://www.democracynow.org/2006/5/5/retired_cia_analyst_ray_mcgovern_takes|accessdate=2021-02-06|date=2006-05-05|publisher=Democracy Now!|language=en|archive-date=2021-03-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210314182741/https://www.democracynow.org/2006/5/5/retired_cia_analyst_ray_mcgovern_takes|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2011年2月，麥高文參加了[[美國國務卿|國務卿]][[希拉蕊·柯林頓|希拉蕊·柯林頓]]在[[喬治華盛頓大學|喬治華盛頓大學]]的演講，並在希拉蕊演講時站起身來、背向希拉蕊，以示對希拉蕊的抗議，他隨即被兩名警察強行拖出場外<ref name=":1">{{Cite web|title=Former CIA Agent Ray McGovern Discusses Arrest at Secretary Clinton's Internet Freedom Speech|url=https://www.huffpost.com/entry/former-cia-agent-ray-mcgo_b_824433|accessdate=2021-02-06|date=2011-02-17|last=Kall|first=Rob|work=HuffPost|language=en|archive-date=2020-08-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200808135534/https://www.huffpost.com/entry/former-cia-agent-ray-mcgo_b_824433|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Ex-CIA Analyst Ray McGovern Beaten, Arrested for Silent Protest at Clinton Speech|url=https://www.democracynow.org/2011/2/18/ex_cia_analyst_ray_mcgovern_beaten|accessdate=2021-02-06|date=2011-02-18|publisher=Democracy Now!|language=en|archive-date=2021-04-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210411044828/https://www.democracynow.org/2011/2/18/ex_cia_analyst_ray_mcgovern_beaten|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=":1" />。2014年，麥高文起訴了這兩名警察、當時處理該起案件的喬治華盛頓大學警局警官以及喬治華盛頓大學<ref>{{Cite web|title=Man who protested 2011 Clinton speech sues UPD officers for excessive force|url=https://www.gwhatchet.com/2014/03/03/man-who-protested-2011-clinton-speech-sues-upd-officers-for-excessive-force/|accessdate=2021-02-06|date=2014-03-03|work=The GW Hatchet|archive-date=2021-02-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210214014045/https://www.gwhatchet.com/2014/03/03/man-who-protested-2011-clinton-speech-sues-upd-officers-for-excessive-force/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2013年10月9日，麥高文與其他三名前情報人員赴[[莫斯科|莫斯科]]，將[[山姆·亞當斯獎|山姆·亞當斯獎]]頒給舉報人[[愛德華·史諾登|愛德華·史諾登]]<ref>{{Cite web|title=“Edward Snowden is a Patriot”: Ex-NSA CIA, FBI and Justice Whistleblowers Meet Leaker in Moscow|url=https://www.democracynow.org/2013/10/14/edward_snowden_is_a_patriot_ex|accessdate=2021-02-06|date=2013-10-14|publisher=Democracy Now!|language=en|archive-date=2021-03-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210308071205/https://www.democracynow.org/2013/10/14/edward_snowden_is_a_patriot_ex|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2014年，麥高文試圖參加前中情局局長[[大衛·裴卓斯|大衛·裴卓斯]]的演講，但遭[[紐約市警察局|紐約市警察局]]拘捕，並被控抵抗逮捕和刑事侵入<ref>{{Cite web|title=Former CIA Analyst Ray McGovern Details Painful Arrest at Petraeus Event|url=https://www.democracynow.org/2014/11/4/headlines/former_cia_analyst_ray_mcgovern_details_painful_arrest_at_petraeus_event|accessdate=2021-02-06|date=2014-11-04|publisher=Democracy Now!|language=en|archive-date=2019-07-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190701160850/https://www.democracynow.org/2014/11/4/headlines/former_cia_analyst_ray_mcgovern_details_painful_arrest_at_petraeus_event|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Former CIA analyst arrested after trying to crash event with David Petraeus|url=https://www.nydailynews.com/new-york/nyc-crime/cia-analyst-arrested-crash-event-david-petraeus-article-1.1996055|accessdate=2021-02-06|date=2014-11-02|last=Tracy|first=Thomas|publisher=New York Daily News|language=en|archive-date=2019-06-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190616162905/https://www.nydailynews.com/new-york/nyc-crime/cia-analyst-arrested-crash-event-david-petraeus-article-1.1996055|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2018年5月9日，時年78歲的麥高文打斷了[[美國參議院|美國參議院]]確認[[吉娜·哈斯佩爾|吉娜·哈斯佩爾]]成為中情局局長的聽證會，大聲喊叫抗議，他立即被[[美國國會警察|國會警察]]強行帶離現場<ref>{{Cite web|title=Police Brutalize 78-Year-Old CIA Whistleblower Protesting at Torturer Gina Haspel’s Senate Hearing|url=https://therealnews.com/police-brutalize-78-year-old-cia-whistleblower-protesting-at-torturer-gina-haspels-senate-hearing|accessdate=2021-02-06|date=2018-05-09|last=McGovern|first=Ray|publisher=The Real News Network|language=en-US|archive-date=2021-05-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210507004117/https://therealnews.com/police-brutalize-78-year-old-cia-whistleblower-protesting-at-torturer-gina-haspels-senate-hearing|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite journal|title=Ray McGovern on Gina Haspel, Torture, and His Recent Arrest|author=|url=https://www.thenation.com/article/archive/ray-mcgovern-on-gina-haspel-torture-and-his-recent-arrest/|last=Carden|first=James|date=2018-05-17|journal=The Nation|language=en-US|access-date=2021-02-06|archive-date=2021-01-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210123055807/https://www.thenation.com/article/archive/ray-mcgovern-on-gina-haspel-torture-and-his-recent-arrest/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

